data.description: Beautiful and inviting two story home with large loft! This home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms and a huge loft that is currently being used as a second family room but could be a 5th bedroom, large office, game room... The options are endless! As you enter, you walk into the formal living room and dining room before you reach the large kitchen that is open to the lower level family room complete with fireplace. Upstairs there are 4 bedrooms plus a loft! The primary bedroom has access to a private balcony with a beautiful view! The backyard is spacious and ready for entertaining, gardening and even possibly an ADU (check with the city). There is an above ground pool that comes with the property perfect for those warm summers! The property has a solar system and a new AC unit! This home is priced to sell so do not wait to come and see!
